gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Suns 97, Timberwolves 87
gameRecap.excerpt: The Phoenix Suns defeated the Minnesota Timberwolves, 97-87. Grayson Allen led the way for Phoenix with 23 points and eight rebounds while Kevin Durant (22 points, six rebounds, six assists) and Devin Booker (13 points, 13 assists) added 35 points. Anthony Edwards led Minnesota with 17 points and eight rebounds in the loss.
